ActFirst Nations Commercial and Industrial Development Act
SubjectMuskowekwan First Nation Solution Potash Mining Regulations
PrecisMUSKOWEKWAN FIRST NATION SOLUTION POTASH MINING REGULATIONS in order to (1) ensure that impacts related to the environment, health and safety, and other impacts common to potash mining are effectively managed; (2) address legislative and regulatory barriers to economic development in First Nations communities; and (3) provide certainty for investors, developers and the public while minimizing costs.
